<Layout title="Start - Aikiwerk" lang="de">
	<main>
		<div class="container">
			<section class="content-section">
				<h2>Start</h2>
				<p>aikiwerk is a Non-Profit Trainingsgemeinschaft for Aikido in Berlin Steglitz.</p>
				<p>We offer joint practice, learning, and exchange. Our focus is on contact work, Aiki principles, and fun in training.</p>
				<p>Visitors are welcome anytime in training.</p>
			</section>
			
			<section class="content-section">
				<h2>English</h2>
				<p>aikiwerk is a non-profit aikido training community in Berlin Steglitz.</p>
